data.description: 2 story 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home on 1.6 acres in beautiful Yosemite Lake Park. This home features an open floor plan with a granite countertop island, 6 burner gas stove with a pot filler for your chef with lots of counter space. All 3 bedrooms are on the second level. The grand bedroom has French doors to your private deck. This property also features a 36ft by 30 1/2 ft detached garage with a 14 ft wide roll up door. This community offers many perks, From, A market, gas station,  hiking/biking trails, golfing, tennis, swimming and an equestrian center, plus more!
